---
// OfferSceneGrowth (Scene 2 · "No phone" · balance + growth chart)
// Source: Figma 5uwYOGoiUbxEw7B8BUv0rv node 10076:61.
// Centered copy above a phone-app-style card built in pure HTML/CSS (no
// screenshots). Shares identical chrome (card, RV logo lockup, avatar) with
// OfferSceneDrain so the two read as the same app.
//
// The ONLY JavaScript on these two scenes lives here: a one-time, on-enter
// animation that grows the three bars from zero and counts the $135,352 figure
// up. It fires once (IntersectionObserver, threshold 0.35), then disconnects.
// The DEFAULT state (no JS, or prefers-reduced-motion) is the FINAL state, so
// nothing is ever hidden without JS; the script sets the collapsed initial
// state itself just before animating.
